Install node.js and npm:sudo apt update
sudo apt install -y nodejs npm
Create the project directory:mkdir project-root
cd project-root
Initialize the project and install packages:npm init -y
npm install express axios express-rate-limit helmet cors csurf cookie-parser sanitize-html @walletconnect/sign-client @walletconnect/modal winston
Install certbot:sudo apt install -y certbot python3-certbot-nginx
Obtain certificates:sudo certbot certonly --standalone -d dcdollarcoin.u